    metaDescription: `PariPulse sharhi 2026: APK va iOS yuklab olish, ro‘yxatdan o‘tish, login, sport tikish, kazino, RTP va jonli bo‘limlar, UZCARD/HUMO to‘lovlar, xavfsizlik hamda hamkorlik va agentlik ma’lumotlari.`,
